Title: Investing 101: A Beginner's Guide | Nikhil Kamath | TEDxBITSHyderabad
Description:
Want to start investing in the stock market with very limited capital? In this talk, Nikhil Kamath, founder of Zerodha and an expert in the field of wealth management, breaks down investing in the stock market for complete beginners, mainly at the college level. He walks us through four distinct approaches to this, and talks about his views on the future of the fintech sector.

üïµÔ∏è‚Äç‚ôÇ‚ÄçCrypto Market Crash CauseüïµÔ∏è‚Äç‚ôÇ‚Äç 

The dip down to 30k was likely institutions intentionally push the price below what most traders believe will be the bottom to scare them into selling their crypto.

üìàBitcoin Dominance Spikesüìà

If the market is crashing and Bitcoin dominance remains low, the potential for a real rebound is likely also low. Keeping this in mind going forward will help you with your trading.

üë∂Fidelity Offers Teenage Investmentüë∂   

Cryptocurrencies do not seem to be on the list of possible investments for the time being, but it‚Äôs likely only a matter of time before the teens who join this program start to ask their parents about Dogecoin.

ü•ïBitcoin Taproot Progressü•ï  

94% of all miners have now signaled their support for the Taproot upgrade which is tentatively scheduled to occur in November this year.

‚õìPolygon And Optimism‚õì    

There is some speculation that Polygon‚Äôs days are numbered. This is because Ethereum‚Äôs ‚Äòin-house‚Äô scaling solution called ‚ÄòOptimism‚Äô seems to be on track for its July launch.

üí∏Parachain Slot Auctionsüí∏   

While Kusama‚Äôs first parachain slot auction is scheduled to occur in the next few days, Polkadot has not yet set a launch date which has some people concerned.

üîéCrypto Tax Crackdownüîé 

Besides the fact that most institutions and individuals report their cryptocurrency activities to the tax man already, these crypto rules requiring you to repot transactions over 10k will not come into force until 2023.

‚öñCrypto Regulations Incoming?‚öñ      

In a short speech at the 2021 FINRA conference, Gary noted that QUOTE ‚Äòthe SEC and FINRA should be ready to bring cases involving issues such as crypto, cyber, and fintech.‚Äô

üê∂Is Elon Musk The Dogecoin Whale? üê∂    

What‚Äôs interesting is that the moment Elon resumed his antics, the Dogecoin whale which holds nearly 30% of its total supply bought 4.2069 DOGE at the same time.

üìäWeekly Crypto Market Analysisüìä   

Interestingly enough, there do seem to be a few cryptos that held up quite well against the downturn. These were Celsius, Polygon, and Solana.
